g.aria-label: As an employee of Cozzi Recycling it is my responsibility to assist in the over-all goal to accomplish our business and QEH&S goals by:
Promote prevention of pollution through good housekeeping practices and timely reporting of all leaks or spills
Exhibit my commitment to customer and supplier satisfaction
Possess knowledge of Industry and Customer Scrap Specifications
Assist in preventing workplace injuries by promptly reporting potential safety risks and all accidents, illnesses and near-misses no matter how small
Exhibit my knowledge of procedures and work instructions
"Chicagoland's Premier Full Service Scrap Recycling Company"
